doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    include ../components/meta.pug
    title= title
  body
    main
      h1 Hello World
      p This application now separates browser-facing pages from JSON API endpoints.
      p The landing page is served from #[code /], while resource endpoints live under #[code /api].
      ul
        li Browse this page at #[a(href='/') /]
        li Fetch all items at #[a(href=apiBasePath) #{apiBasePath}]
        li Organize future HTML routes under #[code src/routes/pages] and API routes under #[code src/routes/api]